T*
(The anomaly classifier uses the engineered feature matrix. The main feature) Tj
T*
(families are:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- region/browser/OS frequency) Tj
T*
(- global ct country frequency) Tj
T*
(- sub-200 ms click flags) Tj
T*
(- local burst density) Tj
T*
(- query entropy) Tj
T*
(- query, domain, and query/domain repetition counts) Tj
T*
(- same-second and exact time-to-click reuse counts) Tj
T*
(- timing magnitude after log transformation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(High-volume domain frequency and global country frequency are down-weighted to 0.50 and) Tj
T*
(0.50, respectively. Events isolated quickly by random hyperplane splits receive higher) Tj
T*
(anomaly scores. EIF is the only production anomaly model; alternate ML backends and) Tj
T*
(supervised pilots have been removed.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
( 5. Thresholds And Decision Logic) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(An event is selected as a bot when either condition is true:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(text) Tj
T*
(combined_score > 0.606846) Tj
T*
(or heuristic_score >= 0.62) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The combined-score threshold is the run-specific 97.5th-percentile cutoff. It) Tj
T*
(keeps the selected volume stable for an unlabelled dataset while letting the ML) Tj
T*
(model influence borderline cases.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The heuristic override protects high-confidence, explainable rule hits. For) Tj
T*
(example, a strongly repeated query/domain pattern with mechanical timing should) Tj
T*
(not be missed only because the anomaly ranking moved after a feature change.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In this run:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- heuristic-only flag rate: 1.40%) Tj
T*
(- ML agreement-tail reference rate: 2.50%) Tj
T*
(- operational confidence estimate: 73%) Tj
T*
ET
